              <p>And now I'm showing my real trading results with my small account every week on <a class="link" href="https://www.youtube.com/@inloopo" target="_blank">my YouTube channel</a>.</p>
              <p>Feel free to check everything out and build confidence.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-item">
            <a>I have little or no trading experience. Will I struggle?</a>
            <div class="content">
