                For those who have no trading experience, it will be very intense. Because you have to learn everything from scratch. But this is also a very good opportunity to learn everything right from the beginning and don't get messed up for example by trading the wrong products like CFDs or Knockout Certificates.</p>
                <p>You will learn everything a professional trader should know and how the pig market participants view the stock markets on the intraday timeframe.</p>
                <p>If you have no trading experience at all, but are excited and motivated to learn, I will give you all my support to become successful. But you need to take your time and have a lot of patience and power to internalize everything.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
